  "slug": "the-trust-and-stability-ceremony",
  "title": "The Trust and Stability Ceremony",
  "subtitle": "A weekly ritual for anchoring unshakeable trust in your relationship with money",
  "excerpt": "A weekly ritual ceremony from Week 10 of the Money Journal program. Works through the five-part ceremony shape with the specific intention of releasing every remaining trace of fear or control around money and allowing deep, settled trust.",
  "type": "PRACTICE",
  "sourceNotes": "Adapted from Week 10 Ritual in MONEY Journal (Rebecca Page, 2025). Used with permission as part of the homemade.education Mindset library.",
  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A weekly ritual for the grip, the constant checking, the bracing for the next problem, the inability to let money sit in the account without a plan attached to it. Works through the five-part ceremony shape: prepare, release, allow, integrate, anchor.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to rituals? Read ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "how rituals work",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "/mindset/how-rituals-work"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " first.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "The practice",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Prepare",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Sit somewhere peaceful. Picture yourself standing on steady ground, not braced, not alert, not waiting for the next thing to go wrong. Just standing.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Release (repeat x3)",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "pullQuote",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "text": "I am ready to release every last trace of fear, instability, or control around money. I release it now. I release it now. I release it now.",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Allow (repeat x3)",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "pullQuote",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "text": "I am ready to align to and allow deep, unshakable trust in money, in life, and in myself. I allow it now. I allow it now. I allow it now.",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Integrate",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Take a slow breath in and all the way out. Picture the ground beneath you as completely solid, your finances, your home, your capacity to handle whatever comes. Steady.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Anchor",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Write this anchor statement in your own handwriting. Say it aloud:",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "pullQuote",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "text": "This week, trust and ease define my relationship with money.",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Where this practice comes from",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Adapted from the Week 10 Ritual in MONEY Journal (Rebecca Page, 2025). Part of the 12-week Money Journal ceremony series.",
            "type": "text"
          }
